OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782317940
OL,3,C'Nanny state' needed to better support
OL,4,Cbabies in first 1001 days
OL,6,FNew legislation is needed to stop
OL,7,Fchildren arriving at school in nappies
OL,8,Fand unable to speak, a veteran
OL,9,FConservative MP has argued.
OL,11,FSir Desmond Swayne admits his
OL,12,Fproposals are "a bit nanny state" but
OL,13,Fsays "sometimes nanny is necessary".
OL,15,FThe MP for New Forest West wants the
OL,16,Fgovernment to be bound by a legal duty
OL,17,Fto provide appropriate information and
OL,18,Fsupport services for children under
OL,19,Ftwo years old.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@aO]uD@FOUuD@cO]
