FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782317940
OL,3,C'Nanny state' needed to better support
OL,4,Cbabies in first 1001 days
OL,6,FHe presented his Infants, Parents and
OL,7,FCarers Bill last week, after coming
OL,8,Ftop in the private members' ballot for
OL,9,Fthe first time in his 29 years in
OL,10,Fparliament.
OL,12,FSir Desmond told ITV News Meridian:
OL,13,F"The babies bill is about the first
OL,14,F1001 days of a child's life.
OL,16,F"It's trying to get much greater
OL,17,Fconcentration on those key days when
OL,18,Fthe baby's brain is forming, when it
OL,19,Freally does need to be nurtured by a
OL,20,Ffamily and to have all the support we
OL,21,Fcan give it."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
