OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782317940
OL,3,C'Nanny state' needed to better support
OL,4,Cbabies in first 1001 days
OL,6,FSecuring first place in the backbench
OL,7,Fballot means Sir Desmond's draft
OL,8,Flegislation has the best opportunity
OL,9,Fto become law of any other MP's
OL,10,Fproposal.
OL,12,FHis decision to use the opportunity
OL,13,Ffor a law focussed on early years
OL,14,Fsupport has been "strongly welcomed"
OL,15,Fby the 1001 Critical Days Foundation.
OL,26,@vD@ROUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
