OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782317940
OL,3,C'Nanny state' needed to better support
OL,4,Cbabies in first 1001 days
OL,6,FThe charity's chief executive, Will
OL,7,FQuince, said: "A baby may be too young
OL,8,Fto understand harm or later put it
OL,9,Finto words, but they are not too young
OL,10,Fto be affected by it. Early
OL,11,Fexperiences do not determine a child's
OL,12,Fdestiny, but they matter profoundly.
OL,14,F"Every parent and carer should be able
OL,15,Fto find trusted support early, before
OL,16,Fdifficulties become crises, so they
OL,17,Fcan give their baby the best start in
OL,18,Flife. Support this important should
OL,19,Fnot be allowed to erode quietly as
OL,20,Fpolitical priorities and budgets
OL,21,Fchange."
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
