OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782317940
OL,3,C'Nanny state' needed to better support
OL,4,Cbabies in first 1001 days
OL,6,FDespite previously arguing for a
OL,7,Fsmaller state, Sir Desmond said the
OL,8,Fcosts of government inaction at a
OL,9,Fyoung age warranted a more proactive
OL,10,Fapproach.
OL,12,F"It's the facts. It's the costs of
OL,13,Fchildren increasingly going to school
OL,14,Fnot nappy trained, not able to speak.
OL,15,FWe've got to address those issues and
OL,16,Fprovide new parents with the support
OL,17,Fthat they need at the time they need
OL,18,Fit.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
