OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782317940
OL,3,C'Nanny state' needed to better support
OL,4,Cbabies in first 1001 days
OL,6,F"Yes, it is a bit nanny state but
OL,7,Fsometimes nanny is necessary." The
OL,8,FTory MP added that he was "confident"
OL,9,Fhis bill would receive cross-party
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FThe Department for Education, which is
OL,13,Fresponsible for early years provision,
OL,14,Fhas been approached for comment.
OL,16,FThe bill is due to be debated in the
OL,17,FHouse of Commons, for what is known as
OL,18,Fits second reading, on 4 September.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@^O]pD@[OUpD@eO]
